snippet.title: Kirby Dream Land for Gameboy Commercial
snippet.description:
A Commercial for Kirbys Dream Land on Gameboy.A Voice Says "We Compare 2 Super Heroes.Dashing Super Guy and Kirby from Nintendo"Kirby Has Nothing.All He's Got is Appetite.The White Puff Ball is Back in Kirbys Dream Land on The Gameboy.
P.S.I Want to Get this Game on my Gameboy.
